Rudy de Leon - Wikipedia






















 






Rudy de Leon

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search



Rudy F. de Leon



Rudy de Leon in 1997






Deputy Secretary of Defense


In office
March 31, 2000 – March 1, 2001[1]


